-- Harvard’s Mullainathan Discusses `Scarcity’ Book (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-09-05T20:49:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-05/harvard-s-mullainathan-discusses-scarcity-book-audio-.html
Sendhil Mullainathan, a professor of
economics at Harvard University, discusses the book, "Scarcity: 
Why Having Too Little Means So Much," of which he is the 
co-author. Mullainathan speaks to Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  on 
Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 11:14
 